summary: So we got this level of heaven with the first kiss and the morning after, how is the fall to hell gonna be when Elliot goes back...
body:
So we got this level of heaven with the first kiss and the morning after, how is the fall to hell gonna be when Elliot goes back to Lucile? When they run into each other. When Elliot tries to speak but no words come out, so he just leaves. When Lucas finds a drawing of Elliot, because that’s the only way he can communicate to him. When Elliot posts sad drawings on his ig. When they look at each other in the distance. Or whatever thing skam has got prepared for us. Imagine if they have to paint the foyer together. All the angst they can throw at us is endless.

My boy Elliot looked so tired after what happened on wednesday, imagine how he is gonna look. I’m not prepared for Lucas to go back to not smiling. This is all gonna wreck us so much.

All with the perfect music, perfect setting, perfect acting, perfect cinematography. Everything perfectly designed to smash our hearts.
